{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"reward"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Image","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI5ImageV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property is used to display a graphical representation of the Offer. For best results, it is recommended to provide images"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in multiple sizes to support different screen resolutions on iOS devices."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should provide 4 versions of the image, with the following dimensions and scale factors:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1x: 300 x 86 pixels"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"2x: 600 x 172 pixels"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"3x: 900 x 258 pixels"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To provide the images, you can add them to an asset catalog by selecting “New Image Set” and setting the name to “offer-reward”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Then, drag and drop the 1x, 2x, and 3x versions of the image into the asset catalog."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Alternatively, you can provide the images with separate filenames, and use the Image(systemName:) method to refer to the appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image in your code. When naming your image files, append “@1x”, “@2x”, or “@3x” to the filename to indicate the scale factor."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"offer-reward@1x (300 x 86 pixels)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"offer-reward@2x (600 x 172 pixels)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"offer-reward@3x (900 x 258 pixels)"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To set the image, you can use the reward property setter or the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reward(_ reward: String)"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Set the image using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reward"},{"type":"text","text":" property"}]}]}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["offer.reward = Image(systemName: \"offer-reward\")"]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Set the image using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"reward(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" method"}]}]}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["offer.reward(\"offer-reward\")"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Providing multiple versions of the image ensures that it looks sharp and clear on all iOS devices,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"regardless of their screen resolution."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/tikisdk\/offer\/reward"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/TikiSdk\/documentation\/TikiSdk\/Offer\/reward","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Image that represents the Offer."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"reward"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"k